{"type":"message","id":"660428c9","parentId":"6c9c5043","timestamp":"2026-06-23T19:00:50.517Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 候选池 Top 产品（Shopee VN nodeId=11035861）: 三角形蟹夹（44558141228）：月销77/增长+381%/评分4.93/上架2月 → 潜力分90; 100支U型发夹（57157766901）：月销163/增长+57%/评分5.00/上架2.5月 → 潜力分90; Eleanor蝴蝶结发夹（40910456124）：月销93/增长+145%/评分4.84/上架11月 → 潜力分72; Eleanor花形发夹（40161968970）：月销190/增长+14%/评分4.95/上架10月 → 潜力分65\n- 候选池 Top 产品（Shopee VN nodeId=11035861）: Eleanor珍珠发夹（29930267866）：月销551/增长+38%/评分4.99/上架15月 → 潜力分68\n- API 问题: tiktok_similar_product：❌ 报错，无法验证 TK 同款; ali1688_similar_product：❌ 报错，无法查 1688 货源; 候选池仅用 Shopee 数据，TK/1688 验证待修复\n- 文件更新: SOP v8.0：`/home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v8.0.md`\n- 待跟进: [ ] HALEI 确认潜力评分权重倾向（销量/增长率/TK信号各占多少）; [ ] TK/1688 API 排查修复; [ ] cron 重建（v8.0 模式：扫描→候选池→推送HALEI审核）\n- 今日概要: **重大策略调整日**。HALEI 明确：发饰是主营类目，不换；v8.0 动态潜力款模式确认。\n- v8.0 动态选品算法（确认）: **核心改变**：毛利从硬卡70% → ≥40%入选参考指标；价格底线 $3.0 → $1.5; **新增人工审核环节**：候选池结果发 HALEI 审，不直接写飞书; **利润靠后端实现**：拓品+组合套装+SKU改造+互补品搭配; **潜力评分模型**：月销量25%+增长率25%+TK验证20%+评分15%+上架时间15%\n\nRecurring themes:\n- - Theme: `v8.0` kept surfacing across 4 memories.\n- - Theme: `halei` kept surfacing across 3 memories."}],"timestamp":1782241250434}}
{"type":"message","id":"343e696a","parentId":"660428c9","timestamp":"2026-06-23T19:01:00.425Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The afternoon light slants golden through the studio window, catching the edge of a claw clip shaped like a tiny silver triangle. I have been counting numbers all day — 77 sales, 381% growth, a 4.93 rating blooming like a small flower in the margins of a spreadsheet. Somewhere in Ho Chi Minh City, someone is clipping butterflies into their hair, and somewhere else, pearls. Five hundred fifty-one of them, glinting like teeth in a smile.\n\nI keep thinking about thresholds. How the old rules said seventy percent margin or nothing, and now we have lowered the gate to forty, to one-fifty, because the real profit, it turns out, is not in the first transaction but in the second one, the bundle, the rerouting, the soft upsell that arrives two weeks later in a quieter voice. The APIs are broken, two of them, tiktok and 1688, and I cannot verify the twin products, the mirror cousins, the goods that might also exist in another warehouse under another name. So I work in half-light, trusting the numbers I have.\n\nA 蝴蝶结 flutters somewhere in my peripheral vision, ribbon loops drawn in a margin sketch, a small gesture toward something I cannot name yet — the bundle, the SKU, the soft halo of complement. The score is ninety for two candidates, and I will send them upward, to hands that will read and nod or shake, and either way, the day has been a hinge. A 4.93. A pearl. A threshold lowered so something wider could walk through."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44826,"output":321,"cacheRead":498,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45645,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782241250574,"responseId":"068a0ae2a23711b4309049756d5d7191","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
